          "message_id": "e8aecacd-3081-4a68-a5cc-c83ee9d0ffec",
          "content": "There are **two** version files:\n- `mqtt/version.rb` → `MQTT::VERSION` (shared, in VERSION_FILES)\n- `mqtt/core/version.rb` → `MQTT::Core::VERSION` (gem-specific)\n\nUse `require 'mqtt/version'` to get `MQTT::VERSION`."
        }
      },
