          "content": "Line 36: when `ref_name` is empty string `\"\"`, it creates `\"0.0.1.pre.\"` instead of `\"0.0.1.pre.unknown\"`.\n\nFix:",
          "tool_uses": [
            {
              "id": "tooluse_0xLZxY5KS9ij1QQ0VRLPJw",
