      "assistant": {
        "ToolUse": {
          "message_id": "74ee946a-91f5-4523-b7a6-697615263729",
          "content": "Yes - `bundler-cache: true` on line 26. The cache might have old gems with `rubocop-rspec` as a transitive dependency.\n\n**Solutions:**\n\n1. **Clear cache** - Add `|| true` to make a dummy change that busts cache:\n2. **Or manually clear** - Go to GitHub repo → Actions → Caches → Delete caches\n3. **Or add explicit cache key** to control versioning\n\nLet's add a cache-busting comment to Gemfile.lock:",
          "tool_uses": [
            {
              "id": "tooluse_LgSqXzdrQH674v6-dLkdtg",
              "name": "execute_bash",
              "orig_name": "execute_bash",
              "args": {
                "summary": "Touch Gemfile to bust cache",
                "command": "cd /home/ggardner/workspace-ruby/async-mqtt && echo \"# Cache bust $(date +%s)\" >> Gemfile && git diff Gemfile"
              },
              "orig_args": {
                "summary": "Touch Gemfile to bust cache",
                "command": "cd /home/ggardner/workspace-ruby/async-mqtt && echo \"# Cache bust $(date +%s)\" >> Gemfile && git diff Gemfile"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
