          "content": "Right - so we need to figure out what's different in the GitHub Actions environment. Let me add debug output to the workflow to see what RuboCop is actually loading:",
          "tool_uses": [
            {
              "id": "tooluse_h0RlF2EUT7yB2sVJNJIXPQ",
              "name": "fs_write",
              "orig_name": "fs_write",
              "args": {
                "summary": "Add debug step to build workflow",
                "path": "/home/ggardner/workspace-ruby/async-mqtt/.github/workflows/build.yml",
                "new_str": "name: Build\non: \n  push:\n  pull_request:\n  workflow_dispatch:\n    inputs:\n      broker_profile:\n        description: 'Mosquitto broker profile'\n        required: false\n        default: 'testing'\n        type: choice\n        options:\n          - stable\n          - testing\n\njobs:\n  test:\n    strategy:\n      fail-fast: false\n      matrix:\n        os: [ubuntu-latest]\n        ruby: ['3.4']\n    runs-on: ${{ matrix.os }}\n    steps:\n    - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n    \n    - uses: ruby/setup-ruby@v1\n      with:\n        ruby-version: ${{ matrix.ruby }}\n        bundler-cache: true\n    \n    - name: Debug RuboCop config\n      run: |\n        find . -name \"*rubocop*\" -type f | grep -v vendor | grep -v .git\n        cat .rubocop.yml\n        bundle exec rubocop --version\n    \n    - name: Start mosquitto broker\n      run: docker compose --profile ${{ github.event.inputs.broker_profile || 'stable' }} up -d\n    \n    - name: Wait for broker\n      run: sleep 3\n    \n    - name: Run build (rubocop, docs, tests)\n      run: bundle exec rake\n    \n    - name: Stop mosquitto broker\n      if: always()\n      run: docker compose --profile ${{ github.event.inputs.broker_profile || 'stable' }} down",
                "old_str": "name: Build\non: \n  push:\n  pull_request:\n  workflow_dispatch:\n    inputs:\n      broker_profile:\n        description: 'Mosquitto broker profile'\n        required: false\n        default: 'testing'\n        type: choice\n        options:\n          - stable\n          - testing\n\njobs:\n  test:\n    strategy:\n      fail-fast: false\n      matrix:\n        os: [ubuntu-latest]\n        ruby: ['3.4']\n    runs-on: ${{ matrix.os }}\n    steps:\n    - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n    \n    - uses: ruby/setup-ruby@v1\n      with:\n        ruby-version: ${{ matrix.ruby }}\n        bundler-cache: true\n    \n    - name: Start mosquitto broker\n      run: docker compose --profile ${{ github.event.inputs.broker_profile || 'stable' }} up -d\n    \n    - name: Wait for broker\n      run: sleep 3\n    \n    - name: Run build (rubocop, docs, tests)\n      run: bundle exec rake\n    \n    - name: Stop mosquitto broker\n      if: always()\n      run: docker compose --profile ${{ github.event.inputs.broker_profile || 'stable' }} down",
                "command": "str_replace"
              },
