        "content": {
          "Prompt": {
            "prompt": "Ahh.. clues...\n2m 19s\nRun bundle exec rake\nrubocop-rspec extension supports plugin, specify `plugins: rubocop-rspec` instead of `require: rubocop-rspec` in /home/runner/work/ruby-mqtt-gems/ruby-mqtt-gems/vendor/bundle/ruby/3.4.0/gems/rubocop-rake-0.7.1/.rubocop.yml.\nFor more information, see https://docs.rubocop.org/rubocop/plugin_migration_guide.html.\nRunning RuboCop...\nAn error occurred while RSpec/AlignLeftLetBrace cop was inspecting /home/runner/work/ruby-mqtt-gems/ruby-mqtt-gems/gems/concurrent_monitor/concurrent_monitor.gemspec.\nTo see the complete backtrace run rubocop -d.\nAn error occurred while RSpec/AlignRightLetBrace cop was inspecting /home/runner/work/ruby-mqtt-gems/ruby-mqtt-gems/gems/concurrent_monitor/concurrent_monitor.gemspec.\nTo see the complete backtrace run rubocop -d.\nAn error occurred while RSpec/AnyInstance cop was inspecting /home/runner/work/ruby-mqtt-gems/ruby-mqtt-gems/gems/concurrent_monitor/concurrent_monitor.gemspec.\nTo see the complete backtrace run rubocop -d."
          }
        },
        "timestamp": "2025-12-07T18:22:22.425014612+01:00",
        "images": null
      },
      "assistant": {
        "ToolUse": {
          "message_id": "c173522d-aef9-4dcf-8d0e-a8c0b49159de",
          "content": "Aha! The issue is that `rubocop-rake` gem itself has a `.rubocop.yml` that requires `rubocop-rspec`, and RuboCop is inheriting from it!\n\nNow that `rubocop-rspec` is installed, it's trying to run RSpec cops on your gemspecs (which aren't RSpec files).\n\nWe need to explicitly disable RSpec cops in your config:",
          "tool_uses": [
            {
              "id": "tooluse_o0aD5gjdRZynOMdR3Koz0w",
              "name": "fs_write",
              "orig_name": "fs_write",
              "args": {
                "summary": "Disable RSpec cops",
                "path": "/home/ggardner/workspace-ruby/async-mqtt/.rubocop.yml",
                "new_str": "AllCops:\n  TargetRubyVersion: 3.4\n  NewCops: enable\n  SuggestExtensions: false\n  Exclude:\n    - 'gems/*/spec/**/*.rb'\n    - 'spec/**/*'\n    - 'benchmark.rb'\n\nplugins:\n  - rubocop-rake\n  - rubocop-minitest\n\nRSpec:\n  Enabled: false\n\nMetrics/ModuleLength:\n  Max: 130\n\nMetrics/ClassLength:\n  Max: 130\n\nMetrics/MethodLength:\n  Max: 15\n\nMetrics/AbcSize:\n  Max: 20\n\nMetrics/CyclomaticComplexity:\n  Max: 10\n\nMetrics/PerceivedComplexity:\n  Max: 10\n\nMetrics/BlockLength:\n  Exclude:\n    - 'Rakefile'\n    - '**/*.rake'",
                "old_str": "AllCops:\n  TargetRubyVersion: 3.4\n  NewCops: enable\n  SuggestExtensions: false\n  Exclude:\n    - 'gems/*/spec/**/*.rb'\n    - 'spec/**/*'\n    - 'benchmark.rb'\n\nplugins:\n  - rubocop-rake\n  - rubocop-minitest\n\nMetrics/ModuleLength:\n  Max: 130\n\nMetrics/ClassLength:\n  Max: 130\n\nMetrics/MethodLength:\n  Max: 15\n\nMetrics/AbcSize:\n  Max: 20\n\nMetrics/CyclomaticComplexity:\n  Max: 10\n\nMetrics/PerceivedComplexity:\n  Max: 10\n\nMetrics/BlockLength:\n  Exclude:\n    - 'Rakefile'\n    - '**/*.rake'",
                "command": "str_replace"
              },
              "orig_args": {
