          "content": "Gemspecs are being checked locally too. The difference might be in how the gems are installed. In CI, gems are in `vendor/bundle`, and RuboCop might be picking up config from `vendor/bundle/ruby/3.4.0/gems/rubocop-rake-0.7.1/.rubocop.yml`.\n\nLet me check if we can tell RuboCop to not inherit from gem configs:",
