          "content": "Excellent theory! Yes, in the GitHub output we saw:\n\n```\n/opt/hostedtoolcache/Ruby/3.4.7/x64/bin/bundle config set --local path /home/runner/work/ruby-mqtt-gems/ruby-mqtt-gems/vendor/bundle\n```\n\nCI installs gems into `./vendor/bundle` (in the working directory), while locally they're in `~/.rvm/gems/`. Let's replicate:",
