          "content": "There it is! Line 175:\n\n```ruby\nrequire async ? \"mqtt/v#{v}/async/client\" : \"mqtt/v#{v}\"\n```\n\nSo the path is `mqtt/v5/async/client` not `mqtt/v5/async`. Let me fix the spec_helper:",
          "tool_uses": [
