          "message_id": "4bb8d6d4-1d2e-4271-b559-f4bd260f13aa",
          "content": "It runs as `user: \"1000:1000\"`. In GitHub Actions, the runner is typically UID 1001. So we need to either:\n1. Remove the user constraint from docker-compose (let it run as root)\n2. Match the user when generating the password file\n\nLet's remove the user constraint since we're in CI:",
