          "content": "Yes, you're UID 1000 locally. But in GitHub Actions, the runner is a different user (typically 1001 or the `runner` user). That's why the `user: \"1000:1000\"` in docker-compose works for you locally but fails in CI.\n\nThe simplest fix is to remove the user constraint so mosquitto runs as root in the container (which can read any file), or make the password file world-readable. Let's do both - remove user constraint and ensure the file is readable:",
