          "content": "Excellent! 🎉 The CI build is passing! \n\nYou now have:\n- ✅ Multi-gem release infrastructure (workflows, version management)\n- ✅ RuboCop passing\n- ✅ YARD documentation building\n- ✅ All tests passing with mosquitto broker in CI\n- ✅ Proper broker lifecycle management\n- ✅ Cross-platform UID/GID handling for docker\n\nNext steps when you're ready:\n1. Merge `ci/release` branch to `main`\n2. Set up `RUBYGEMS_API_KEY` secret in GitHub repo settings\n3. Create \"release\" environment in GitHub\n4. Test the pre-release workflow: `rake version:tag_prerelease`\n5. Do your first release: bump version, tag, and push\n\nGreat work debugging all those CI issues! The project is now well set up for continuous integration and releases."
