    "> You don't have my github auth. I will do the final push separately. Is that ready to go?",
    "Yes, ready! Here are the commands for you to run:\n\n```bash\ncd /home/ggardner/workspace-ruby/async-mqtt\ngit checkout -b ci/release\ngit add -A\ngit commit -m \"ci: add release workflows and version management\"\ngit push -u origin ci/release\n```\n\nThis will:\n- Create `ci/release` branch\n- Commit all the release infrastructure + version fixes\n- Push to GitHub\n\nAfter that, you can test the pre-release workflow or merge to main first.\n[Tool uses: none]",
